  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\"><img alt=\"House Yronwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/50px-House_Yronwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/75px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/100px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Gwyneth Yronwood</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\"><img alt=\"House Yronwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/50px-House_Yronwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/75px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/100px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Gwyneth_Yronwood_01.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Gwyneth Yronwood 01.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/Gwyneth_Yronwood_01.png/300px-Gwyneth_Yronwood_01.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/Gwyneth_Yronwood_01.png/450px-Gwyneth_Yronwood_01.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8b/Gwyneth_Yronwood_01.png/600px-Gwyneth_Yronwood_01.png 2x\" /></a><div>Gwyneth Yronwood at her needlework.</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\">House Yronwood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_287_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">287&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_288_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">288&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Anders_Yronwood\" title=\"Anders Yronwood\">Anders Yronwood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gwyneth Yronwood</b> is the youngest daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Anders_Yronwood\" title=\"Anders Yronwood\">Anders Yronwood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gwyneth_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>At twelve years old, she is a small, scrawny girl whose dark eyes and brown hair set her apart in a house of blue-eyed blondes. She is clever and as quick with words as with her hands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gwyneth_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Martell\" title=\"Quentyn Martell\">Quentyn Martell</a> was <a href=\"/index.php/Fosterage\" title=\"Fosterage\">fostered</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Yronwood\" title=\"Yronwood\">Yronwood</a>, Gwyneth became fond of him and hoped to marry him after she had <a href=\"/index.php/Flowering\" title=\"Flowering\">flowered</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gwyneth_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gwyneth_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Her older brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Cletus_Yronwood\" title=\"Cletus Yronwood\">Cletus</a>, has recently passed while traveling with Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Martell\" title=\"Quentyn Martell\">Quentyn Martell</a> on his mission to meet with <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gwyneth_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I want to go back to <a href=\"/index.php/Yronwood\" title=\"Yronwood\">Yronwood</a> and kiss both of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Drinkwater\" title=\"House Drinkwater\">your sisters</a>, marry Gwyneth Yronwood, watch her flower into beauty, have a child by her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Martell\" title=\"Quentyn Martell\">Quentyn Martell</a>'s thoughts in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gwyneth_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\"